{{VoidedTheme}}
<div class="titleblock"><span style="font-family:Jost;">
<div class="blurquote-noperson">
{{Blurquote|image=Infinite hotel hallway.png|quote-text=I heard the desperate cries of what I thought to be a person in despair. I rushed to the source as quick as possible, but when I got there, all that was in front of my eyes was a white, innocent looking exit door, creaking as it slowly opened outwards, revealing pure blackness beyond its wrath.
